Software Requirements Specifications (SRS) for Contact Manager App

Definitions, Acronyms, and Abbrevriations
Contact Manager     |       The name of the app.
SMS                 |       Short Method Service

Functional Requirements
 1. The app shall allow users to manage contacts.
   1.1 The app shall allow a user to add a contact.
   1.2 The app shall allow a user to view a contact. 
   1.3 The app shall allow a user to edit a contact.
   1.4 The app shall allow a user to delete a contact.
   1.5 The app shall allow a user to group contacts.
 2. The app shall allow users to communicate with contacts.
   2.1 The app shall allow users to send an SMS to a contact.
   2.2 The app shall allow users to make a phone call to a contact.
 3. The app shall allow users persistent access to contacts.
   3.1 The app shall store contacts data on close.
   3.2 The app shall store contacts on restart.
   3.3 The app shall store contacts on unexpected close.  
   
